    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="IELTS-Vocabulary"><a href="#IELTS-Vocabulary" class="headerlink" title="IELTS Vocabulary"></a>IELTS Vocabulary</h1><h3 id="Word-list-1"><a href="#Word-list-1" class="headerlink" title="Word list 1"></a>Word list 1</h3><p><strong>词根、词缀</strong></p><ol><li>sorb 吸收</li><li>sent 送</li><li>solut 松开</li><li>us 使用</li><li>tarct 拉，抽</li><li>celer 快速的</li><li>cess 走</li><li>cumul 堆积</li><li>bat 走</li><li>apt 适合的</li></ol><p><strong>单词</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>abate</strong> v. 减轻，降价</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>a(加强) + bate(减弱，减少) </p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​This action can’t <em><strong>abate</strong></em> his bad habits.</p></li><li><p><strong>abhorrent</strong> adj. 可恶的，可恨的</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>ab(加强) + horr(发抖) + ent(形容词后缀)</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​Ever since he started stealing, He’s been <em><strong>abhorrent</strong></em>.</p></li><li><p><strong>abide</strong> v. 遵守，逗留；容忍，忍受</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>a (加强)+ bide(停留)</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​We need to <em><strong>abide</strong></em> the law, else we will be punished.</p></li><li><p><strong>abode</strong>* n. 房屋，家</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>right of abode 居住权; fixed abode 固定住所</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​I enjoy to living in my small but cozy <em><strong>abode</strong></em>.</p></li><li><p><strong>abound</strong>*  vi. 丰富，充满</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>a(一个) + bound(界限，范围) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>  所有物品都在一个区<span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>域内  丰富，充满</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​My computer drive is <em><strong>abound</strong></em> with galgame.</p></li><li><p><strong>absenteeism</strong>* n. 旷课；旷工</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>absent + ee(代表人) + ism <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 旷课；旷工</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​The China company dislike their sutff have <em><strong>absenteeism</strong></em>, because it will dcrease the productivity.</p></li><li><p><strong>absolute</strong>* adj. 完全的，绝对的，纯粹的</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>ab(加强) + solut(松开) + e <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 完全松开 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 完全的，信任的</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​Your answer was <em><strong>absolute</strong></em> incorrect.</p></li><li><p><strong>absorb</strong>* v. 吸收；吸引…的注意，使全神贯注</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>ab(离去) + sorb(吸收) + <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 吸掉 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 吸收</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​He <em><strong>absorb</strong></em> teacher attention by shout the correct answer out.</p></li><li><p><strong>abstract</strong>* adj. 抽象的</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span>abs + tract <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 抽象化</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​The extand math is partly <em><strong>abstract</strong></em>.</p><ol><li><strong>abstraction</strong> n. 抽象</li></ol></li><li><p><strong>absurd</strong>* adj. 荒谬的，荒唐的</p><p> <span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> Currently, the societies is absurd.</p></li><li><p><strong>abundance</strong>* n. 大量，丰富，充足，充裕</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 来自<em><strong>abundant</strong></em> (adj. 丰富的，充裕的)</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> At the party, there was food and drink in <em><strong>abundance</strong></em>.</p></li><li><p><strong>academic</strong>* adj. 学院的；学术的；不切实际的；n. 学者；大学教授</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> The <em><strong>academic</strong></em> research what we are doing now will impact our GPA.</p></li><li><p><strong>accelerate</strong> v. 加速；促进</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac(=to) + celer(快速的) + ate(使…) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 加速；促进</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> He’s <em><strong>accelerating</strong></em> our productivity.</p></li><li><p><strong>accessible</strong> adj. 能接近的；易达到的</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> He pointed his telescope to every <em><strong>accessible</strong></em> part of the sky and recorded what he saw.</p></li><li><p><strong>accessory</strong>* n. 附件，零件；服装搭配物，装饰品；同谋，帮凶</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ​ac(附近) + cess(走) + ory <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 接近主题的部分 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 附件，零件 :</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> My sister buys a lot of <em><strong>accessories</strong></em> but doesn’t use these. </p></li><li><p><strong>acclaim</strong>* vt. 向…欢呼，为…喝彩 n. 称赞；欢迎</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac(向) + claim(大声欢呼) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 想某人大声叫喊 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 为…欢呼</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> There’s lots to see and to do, including the internationally- <em><strong>acclaimed</strong></em> climbing wall built on the site of the old aquarium.</p></li><li><p><strong>acclimatise</strong>* v. 适应新环境</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> After a couple of days to <em><strong>acclimatise</strong></em> yourself, you’ll start the trek on day three walking through the enormous Katiba Forest which will take the whole of the day.</p></li><li><p><strong>accommodation</strong>* n. 住处</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac + commod(看作common, 普通的) + ation(名词后缀) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 再普通的人都需要住处 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 住处 </p></li><li><p><strong>accompany</strong>* vt. 陪伴；伴随, 于同时发生；伴奏</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac(表加强) + company(同伴; 陪伴) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 陪伴；伴随</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> I <em><strong>accompany</strong></em> the animation girl that in galgame, when other accompany their real girl friend. <span class="github-emoji"><span>😭</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f62d.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span></p></li><li><p><strong>accomplish</strong> vt. 达到(目的)，完成(任务)，实现(计划、诺言等)</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac + compl(看作complete，完成) + ish(使…) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 完成</p><p>Eventually, I <em><strong>accomplished</strong></em> what I set out to do when I was 8 years old.</p></li><li><p><strong>accountancy</strong> n. 会计工作，会计职业</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> My father worked in <em><strong>accountancy</strong></em> and helps his company avoid unnecessary cost.</p><p><strong>accountant</strong> n. 会计师 </p></li><li><p><strong>accredit</strong> vt. 信任，相信，为人，授权；把…归于</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac + credit(信任) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 信任，相信</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> Our company’s goal is for every employee <em><strong>accredit</strong></em> each other.</p></li><li><p><strong>accreditation</strong>* n. 证明合格，检定合格</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 来自accredit</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> Our school has already reached the standards for the <em><strong>accreditation</strong></em> of colleges.</p></li><li><p><strong>accumulate</strong>* v. 积累；堆积</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac(表加强) + cumul(堆积) + ate <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 不断堆积 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 积累</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> I accumulate a lots of Galgame in my pc. <span class="github-emoji"><span>😆</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f606.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span></p></li><li><p><strong>accustom</strong>* vt. 使习惯于</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac(表加强) + custom(风俗，习惯) <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 使成为习惯 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 使习惯于</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> If you go abroad for further study it will take a period of time for you to <em><strong>accustom</strong></em> yourself to the new environment, the new culture and all the new rules and regulations.</p></li><li><p><strong>acknowledge</strong>* v. 承认，确认；致意；感谢</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>⭐</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2b50.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> ac + know(知道)  + ledge <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 大家都有的知识 <span class="github-emoji"><span>➡</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/27a1.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> 承认</p><p><span class="github-emoji"><span>ℹ</span><img src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2139.png?v8" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.parent.classList.add('github-emoji-fallback')"></span> Without acknowledge it, we can’t finish this project.</p></li><li></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
